FLUID RESPONSIVE DESIGN WITHOUT BREAKPOINTS

Characteristics:

	- No jumps while changing size of any page element.
	- Design sizes and spaced in relation to base font size.
	- Does not solve jumps in layout change.
	- No upper and lower limits.

Applications:

	- Whole website.
	- Widget, graph, visualisation.
	- Scaling based on parent element size.
	- Scale in both width and height.

Technical:

	- Use rem, em; px only if necessary.
	- Media aspect ratio for layout changes.
	- Some math is involved.
